subtitle: Percent of electoral votes divided by percent population for each state
Hover around each state to see their value

tooltip.signal: {"State": isValid(datum["State"]) ? datum["State"] : ""+datum["State"], "% electoral votes divided by % population": format(datum["votes-population"], "")}

description.signal: "votes-population: " + (format(datum["votes-population"], "")) + "; centroid_lat: " + (format(datum["centroid_lat"], "")) + "; centroid_lon: " + (format(datum["centroid_lon"], "")) + "; votes-population (binned): " + (!isValid(datum["bin_maxbins_10_votes-population"]) || !isFinite(+datum["bin_maxbins_10_votes-population"]) ? "null" : format(datum["bin_maxbins_10_votes-population"], "") + " – " + format(datum["bin_maxbins_10_votes-population_end"], "")) + "; State: " + (isValid(datum["State"]) ? datum["State"] : ""+datum["State"]) + "; % electoral votes divided by % population: " + (format(datum["votes-population"], ""))
